section#gallery
    .container
        .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-8
                .title.reveal_bottom
                    h1.text-red What I do
                    p 目前從事網頁設計，喜歡設計、摸索前端語言；喜歡設計後，再透過程式一步一步建構出畫面、動畫；覺得那是有趣、具有成就感的。

        .row.justify-content-center.reveal_bottom
            .col-lg-8
                .swiper-container.image-swiper
                    .swiper-wrapper
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-1.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-2.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-3.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-4.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-5.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')
                        .swiper-slide
                            img(src="img/debby_dailyUI_design-6.png", alt='Debby design | UI design')

                    .swiper-pagination
        .row.justify-content-center.reveal_bottom
            .col-lg-8.d-flex
                .swiper-button
                    .swiper-prev
                        include ../../img/arrow-left.svg

                    .swiper-next
                        include ../../img/arrow-right.svg
                .see-more
                    p See more...
                    a(href="https://dailydesignfromdebby.tumblr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Design
                    a(href="https://debbyillustrations.tumblr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Illustration